message.content:
**__Why is Steam redownloading the game each update?__**

Steam is only downloading the required patch files, but will verify all the game files.
This means that it will appear as 30gb+ update.

**__Why says Steam the download will take several days?__**

Update-time can be incorrectly displayed due to how Windows handles multiple small files, both when updating and validating the files.
In most cases the time shown will not be correct when it displays an extremely long installation-time. It usually also shows a longer time on a normal HDD compared to a SSD
